casebody.data:
Vella TRADER, Personal Representative of the Estate of Thelma L. DeGoede, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
COMERICA BANK, f/k/a, Industrial State Bank & Trust Company, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158487
COA: 339577 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 2, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's February 4, 2019 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that reconsideration of our previous order is warranted. MCR 7.311(G).
